{
  "_note": "日报卡片模板参考。生成日报 JSON 时拷贝此结构、替换占位符，写入 /tmp/daily_report.json 后调 feishu_post.py。",
  "_header_template_options": "blue(推荐) / red(紧急) / green(全绿) / yellow / grey / purple",
  "_lark_md_tricks": "支持 **加粗** · `inline code` · <font color='red'>红</font> · <font color='green'>绿</font> · [link](url) · \\n 换行",

  "card": {
    "config": {"wide_screen_mode": true},
    "header": {
      "title": {"tag": "plain_text", "content": "📊 供应商内容池校验 · 实时日报"},
      "subtitle": {"tag": "plain_text", "content": "数据截至：{YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM} · 口径=全量存量池"},
      "template": "blue"
    },
    "elements": [
      {"tag": "markdown", "content": "**🔥 当前异常趋势 Top 3**"},
      {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🎉 **{cp}** · `{field}` 空：{X} → **{Y}**（<font color='green'>-{pct}%</font>）\n⚠️ **{cp}** · `{field}` 空：{X} → {Y}（<font color='red'>{原因}</font>）"}},
      {"tag": "hr"},

      {"tag": "markdown", "content": "**📋 CP 总览（全量存量）**"},
      {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "columns": [
        {"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "vertical_align": "top", "elements": [
          {"tag": "markdown", "content": "🚨 **guoying**"},
          {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "总量 **{N}**\n紧急 {X} · 高 {Y}"}}
        ]},
        {"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "vertical_align": "top", "elements": [
          {"tag": "markdown", "content": "🚨 **dihui**"},
          {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "总量 **{N}**\n紧急 {X} · 高 {Y}"}}
        ]},
        {"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "vertical_align": "top", "elements": [
          {"tag": "markdown", "content": "⚠️ **beike**"},
          {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "总量 **{N}**\n紧急 {X} · 高 {Y}"}}
        ]},
        {"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "vertical_align": "top", "elements": [
          {"tag": "markdown", "content": "✅ **meilaoban**"},
          {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "总量 **{N}**\n低 {Y}"}}
        ]}
      ]},
      {"tag": "hr"},

      {"tag": "markdown", "content": "**🚨 {cp_name} · {N} 条**"},
      {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "· `{field}`（{业务含义}）空 · <font color='red'>**{N}**</font>\n· 作者映射 lead→多 author：{X} keys / {Y} items"}},
      {"tag": "hr"},

      {"tag": "markdown", "content": "**📎 近期修复亮点**"},
      {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "· beike `publish_time`：{X} → {Y}（清理内容）\n· dihui `author_image`：{X} → {Y}（一日内变化）"}},

      {"tag": "markdown", "content": "**⏳ 遗留主要问题（推 CP）**"},
      {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "1. **{cp}** · `{field}` {N} 条 / ...\n2. ..."}},

      {"tag": "note", "elements": [{"tag": "plain_text", "content": "数据来源：paimon_zjyprc_hadoop.browser.business_content_pool_realtime · 跑数时间 {YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM}"}]}
    ]
  }
}
